snippet: Nate Schierholtz hit a two-out game-ending RBI single, after Chris Coghlan homered to tie it in the eighth, and the Chicago Cubs beat the New York Mets 2-1 on Tuesday night....

headline.print_headline: Schierholtz, Cub Beat Mets 2-1 in 9th Inning
headline.main: Schierholtz, Cub Beat Mets 2-1 in 9th Inning

lead_paragraph: Nate Schierholtz hit a two-out game-ending RBI single, after Chris Coghlan homered to tie it in the eighth, and the Chicago Cubs beat the New York Mets 2-1 on Tuesday night.
